;重写pclogo时代的读取数组指令
;命令版本号v1.4

to hair.old.aget :a :v
hair.detect
if and (not word? :a) (not array? :a) [hair.debug.error "获取数组语法错误 stop]
if and list? :v 1=count :v [make "v first :v]
if word? :a [make "a thing :a]
ifelse list? :v [op mditem map [? + 1] :v :a][op item :v+1 :a]
end
bury "hair.old.aget
